  "title": "Sales Executive / Sales Representative",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $2500 - $3000 + Allowance + Commission + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Woodlands</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: Monday to Friday (8.30am to 5.30pm)</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Actively prospect and generate new leads through networking, cold calling, and leveraging existing industry contacts to ensure maximum sales opportunities locally and overseas</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Understand customer needs and provide appropriate solutions that align with company offerings</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Achieve and execute sales strategies to meet or exceed monthly sales targets</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Build and maintain strong relationships with new and existing clients</strong></li>\n  <li>Preparing weekly and monthly reports</li>\n  <li>Provide exceptional customer service and ongoing client support</li>\n  <li>Take initiative to stay up to date with our offerings and keep informed of market trends and industry developments</li>\n  <li>Provide trustworthy feedback and after-sales support, continuously improve through feedback</li>\n  <li>Weekly/monthly sales report submission to respective superiors</li>\n  <li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess minimum Diploma or Degree in business, marketing, economics, or related field is an advantage</li>\n  <li><strong>Possess minimum 2 years in sales (B2B preferred)</strong></li>\n  <li>Possess own vehicle will be an advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
